<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Game Archives</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .header { background-color: #4a4a4a; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 2em 0; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.5em; }
        .container { width: 80%; margin: 2em auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2em; }
        .game-card { background-color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; text-align: center; transition: transform 0.2s; }
        .game-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .game-card img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; }
        .game-info { padding: 1.5em; }
        .game-info h2 { font-size: 1.5em; margin-top: 0; }
        .game-info p { font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; }
        .home-link { display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 2em; font-size: 1.1em; color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; }
        .home-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>The Game Archives</h1>
        <p>A journey through the history of online gaming.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="game-card">
            <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0204657/?ref_=ls_t_1" target="_blank">
                <img src="/images/super-mario-64.jpg" alt="Super Mario 64 box art">
            </a>
            <div class="game-info">
                <h2>Super Mario 64 (1996)</h2>
                <p>One of the most influential games of its time, pioneering the 3D platformer genre with a free-roaming camera and a non-linear world.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="game-card">
            <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0286598/?ref_=ls_t_2" target="_blank">
                <img src="/images/doom.jpg" alt="Doom poster">
            </a>
            <div class="game-info">
                <h2>Doom (1993)</h2>
                <p>The grandfather of first-person shooters, Doom pioneered networked multiplayer deathmatches and set the stage for online gaming as we know it.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="game-card">
            <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0208155/?ref_=ls_t_3" target="_blank">
                <img src="/images/final-fantasy-7.jpg" alt="Final Fantasy VII box art">
            </a>
            <div class="game-info">
                <h2>Final Fantasy VII (1997)</h2>
                <p>This JRPG became a global sensation, known for its cinematic storytelling, deep characters, and groundbreaking graphics on the PlayStation console.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="game-card">
            <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0308956/?ref_=ls_t_6" target="_blank">
                <img src="/images/system-shock-2.jpg" alt="System Shock 2 poster">
            </a>
            <div class="game-info">
                <h2>System Shock 2 (1999)</h2>
                <p>A cult classic that masterfully blended RPG elements with survival horror, praised for its immersive atmosphere and complex narrative.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="game-card">
            <a href="https://worldofwarcraft.blizzard.com/en-gb/" target="_blank">
                <img src="/images/world-of-warcraft.jpg" alt="World of Warcraft poster">
            </a>
            <div class="game-info">
                <h2>World of Warcraft (2004)</h2>
                <p>WoW exploded onto the scene, popularizing the MMORPG genre and becoming a cultural phenomenon with its accessible gameplay and rich lore.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="home-link">Go back to Home</a>
</body>
</html>